text: Neumünster (Low Saxon: Niemünster, Neemünster; North Frisian: Naimünster) is a city in the middle of Schleswig-Holstein, Germany. In 2015 about 79,000 people lived there. The city is located at the river Schwale. The Aukrug Nature Park is close to the town. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Cities in Schleswig-Holstein
title: Neumünster
